Fourth Department,

December, 1966

(December 1,1966) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Wallace Mabry, Appellant.

Order unanimously affirmed. (See People v. Nicholson,

11 N Y 2d 1067.) (Appeal from order of Monroe County Court denying, without a hearing, motion for a rehearing on a motion to vacate a judgment of conviction for robbery and other felonies, entered November 22, 1962.) Present — Bastow, J. P., Goldman, Henry, Del Vecchio and Marsh, JJ.
